entries.femaleVariant: Well, my friend's grandmother swears by her violet crystal. When it gets really bad, she rubs it on the spot.
Helps? Saved her life, more than once. Even had her do an interview once down at the studio. Dunno why they never aired it.
Of course they didn't air it. The corporations are all afraid of the truth. But the results speak for themselves.
Exactly! They get sick, they'll change their tune.
Mhm. These days, all this technology everywhere, I mean it's really no wonder we're all falling apart.
